&gt; On Tue, 25 Feb 2025 at 00:26, Domenic Denicola &lt;dome...@chromium.org&gt;
&gt; wrote:
&gt;
&gt;&gt; Thanks for this attention to detail! A few minor points:
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; On Tue, Feb 25, 2025 at 12:52 AM Stephen McGruer &lt;smcgr...@chromium.org&gt;
&gt;&gt; wrote:
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt; Note: We've done outreach to the WPWG members (
&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://lists.w3.org/Archives/Public/public-payments-wg/2025Feb/0008.html"&gt;https://lists.w3.org/Archives/Public/public-payments-wg/2025Feb/0008.html&lt;/a&gt;),
