&lt;pre&gt;For the record, feature detection/fallback can work thusly:

&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://codepen.io/mysterydate/pen/zxYKReo"&gt;https://codepen.io/mysterydate/pen/zxYKReo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;

If the user sets a valid gradient, then attempts to set with one of the new 
color spaces but those are not yet available, the CSS background property 
will not be set.

