&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;tt&gt;&lt;a rel="nofollow" href="https://launch.corp.google.com/launch/4320162"&gt;https://launch.corp.google.com/launch/4320162&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;&lt;&lt;a rel="nofollow" href="https://launch.corp.google.com/launch/4320162"&gt;https://launch.corp.google.com/launch/4320162&lt;/a&gt;&gt; &lt;/tt&gt;&lt;pre style="margin: 0em;"&gt;
Measurement
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;tt&gt;Originally measured rel=”payment” in &lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;&lt;a rel="nofollow" href="https://chromestatus.com/metrics/feature/timeline/popularity/4976"&gt;https://chromestatus.com/metrics/feature/timeline/popularity/4976&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;&lt;&lt;a rel="nofollow" href="https://chromestatus.com/metrics/feature/timeline/popularity/4976"&gt;https://chromestatus.com/metrics/feature/timeline/popularity/4976&lt;/a&gt;&gt;before &lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;the project changed to rel=”facilitated-payment”. The measurement for &lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;rel=”facilitated-payment” is not available yet. &lt;/tt&gt;&lt;pre style="margin: 0em;"&gt;
