&gt;  
&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://wpt.fyi/results/content-security-policy/worker-src/shared-worker-src-child-fallback-blocked.sub.html?label=experimental&amp;label=master&amp;aligned"&gt;https://wpt.fyi/results/content-security-policy/worker-src/shared-worker-src-child-fallback-blocked.sub.html?label=experimental&amp;label=master&amp;aligned&lt;/a&gt;
&gt;  
&gt; Note that the test code currently has the wrong expectation and will be 
&gt; updated as part of this feature work.
