&gt;
&gt; Summary
&gt;
&gt; This is a combined Intent to ship for the following features:
&gt;
&gt; ::scroll-marker and ::scroll-marker-group for scrolling containers:
&gt;
&gt; Pseudo elements that allow to create a set of focusable markers for all of
&gt; the associated items within the scrolling container.
&gt;
&gt; ::scroll-button(&lt;direction&gt;):
&gt;
&gt; Focusable pseudo-element button that allows scrolling the scrolling
&gt; container in the associated direction.
&gt;
&gt; ::column
&gt;
&gt; Supports associating ::scroll-marker elements with column fragments and
&gt; scroll snap aligning to columns.
&gt;
&gt; Explainer
&gt;
&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://chrome.dev/carousel/"&gt;https://chrome.dev/carousel/&lt;/a&gt;
&gt;
&gt;
&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/blob/main/css-overflow-5/carousel-explainer.md"&gt;https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/blob/main/css-overflow-5/carousel-explainer.md&lt;/a&gt;
&gt;
&gt; Specification
&gt;
&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-overflow-5/#scroll-navigation"&gt;https://drafts.csswg.org/css-overflow-5/#scroll-navigation&lt;/a&gt;
&gt;
&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-multicol-2/#column-pseudo"&gt;https://drafts.csswg.org/css-multicol-2/#column-pseudo&lt;/a&gt;
