&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; or interop issues. Please list open issues (e.g. links to known github
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; issues in the project for the feature specification) whose resolution 
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; may
