&gt;&gt;&gt; I'd like to check back in on this deprecation. The drop in usage from
&gt;&gt;&gt; May continued into June and July, with current numbers hovering around
&gt;&gt;&gt; 0.003%:
&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://chromestatus.com/metrics/feature/timeline/popularity/3874"&gt;https://chromestatus.com/metrics/feature/timeline/popularity/3874&lt;/a&gt;. I
&gt;&gt;&gt; added deprecation messages in M127, but that's not even in stable yet. My
&gt;&gt;&gt; guess would be that usage will continue to drop as 127 goes to stable.
&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt; Given the above, I'd like to re-request permission to remove the feature
&gt;&gt;&gt; in M129, assuming all of the trends continue to look good.
