&gt;&gt;&gt; Specification&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://w3c.github.io/webauthn/#publickeycredential"&gt;https://w3c.github.io/webauthn/#publickeycredential&lt;/a&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt; Summary
&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt; The WebAuthn PublicKeyCredential.toJSON(), 
&gt;&gt;&gt; parseCreationOptionsFromJSON() and parseRequestOptionsFromJSON() methods 
&gt;&gt;&gt; let developers serialize a WebAuthn response into a JSON object or 
&gt;&gt;&gt; deserialize a WebAuthn request object from its JSON representation.
&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt; Blink componentBlink&gt;WebAuthentication 
&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://bugs.chromium.org/p/chromium/issues/list?q=component:Blink%3EWebAuthentication"&gt;https://bugs.chromium.org/p/chromium/issues/list?q=component:Blink%3EWebAuthentication&lt;/a&gt;&gt;
